          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1672754305289-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>spiced stock </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>to the pan with a grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook, covered, for 5-6 min or until the veg is tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1672754309353-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1672754309353-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1672754309353-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1672754309353-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1672754309353-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for a final 1-2 min or until wilted – this is your <strong>gochujang chicken thigh stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1672754351434-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
