            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>gochujang chicken thigh stew </strong>and<strong> sticky rice</strong> in separate bowls</p><p>Garnish the stew with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
